==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fleeting
<hw>Fleet"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Passing swiftly away; not
durable; transient; transitory; <as>as, the <ex>fleeting</ex> hours or
moments</as>.</def></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Evanescent; ephemeral. See
<er>Transient</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fleetingly</ent>⟦br⟧
